        <key>Policy Action Script Text</key>
        <language>en</language>
        <message>&lt;ul&gt;&lt;li&gt;Form values must be modified in the function  &lt;b style="font-size:14px;"&gt;customScripts&lt;/b&gt;. User data cannot be overwritten with scripts, but is available to use in script conditions. An example script is:   &lt;br&gt;&#13;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;var groups = this.parameters.userData.groups;&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;if( groups.length &gt; 0){&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;formData.App_Server_NodeName = "MyNodeName";&lt;br&gt;&#13;
&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;}&lt;br&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;li&gt;Changes in any other function could result in an error and thus cancellation of requested catalog item.&lt;/li&gt;&#13;
&lt;/ul&gt;</message>
